  <brief_title>Percutaneous Coronary Intervention (PCI) With Drug-Eluting Stents (DES) Versus Coronary Artery Bypass Graft (CABG) for Patients With Significant Left Main Stenosis</brief_title>
  <official_title>PCI With DES Versus CABG for Patients With Significant Left Main Stenosis</official_title>
  <sponsors>
